            <li><a href="#">You must confirm your e-mail.<span class="mif-mail icon"></span></a></li>    @*Must be href to profile*@
            <li><a href="#">You must be registered on the site for more than a week.<span class="mif-calendar icon"></span></a></li>
            <li class="divider"></li>
            <li><a href="#"><span class="mif-books icon"></span>Example AD.</a></li>  @*Must be href to example page*@
            <li><a href="#"><span class="mif-help icon"></span>Help.</a></li> @*Must be href to page help*@
        </ul>
    </div>
    @*<h3> Before you add your advertisement you must do few this requirements:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>You must be logged in.</li>
            <li>You must confirm your e-mail.</li>
            <li>You must be registered on the site for more than a week.</li>
        </ul>*@
</div>

